column5: Only had 4 hits all day.....all four fish were good ones.....  got this 10 pounder while jigging with a hedden sonar............      got this 10 1/2 pound walleye trolling with a reef runner..........    got this 12 pound pike while trolling with a deep reef runner........    here is Lund06 with a 14 pound walleye caught while trolling with a deep reef runner.........
nice going  they are beautiful fish
What you figure those fish swam all the way from NY so you came to take them back ???  LOL  Some great fish in tough conditions fella.
WOW, talking about hardcore fishing!
awesome day Doug!
Very Nice :thumbsup_anim: Richard
thanks wayne some say the big ones on the niagara bar are from quinte
Awesome stuff, vette!  Fish like that help you stay warm
Nice slabs 'vette.
Wow Corvy!!!  Not many hits but quality fish for sure Great job you two and thanks for sharing Jacques
well done! Not many 14 lbs taken this year
Nice fish Corvy....man it looks cold out there.......did i just say nice fish?....oooops...i meant to say AWESOME FISH!
I swear that fish was following my lure the other day  but he missed it Way to go guys.
Nice! x4!!!!
thanks johnny b  thanks    thanks fishhuter big ones were hard to catch
SweeeeeeeeeeeT, great catches there  Congratz
Great fish. Love the looks of that pike, so clean looking.
very nice , well worth the effort you put in
Good shoot'n Doug, love that you nailed a good one jigging.
Good report, thanks for sharing.  Some real trophies there.
